      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u8FEB\u308A\u6765\u308B\u767D\u3044\u5F71",
        "Client": "\u3068\u3042\u308B\u30A2\u30A4\u30EB\u30FC\u306E\u65E5\u8A8C",
        "Description": "\u3046\uFF5E\u3001\u5BD2\u3044\u30CB\u30E3\u2026\u51CD\u3048\u308B\u30CB\u30E3\u2026\u3002\r\n\u5BD2\u3059\u304E\u3066\u3001\u5E7B\u304C\u898B\u3048\u3066\u304D\u305F\u30CB\u30E3\u2026\r\n\u767D\u304F\u3066\u76EE\u304C\u306A\u304F\u3066\u3001\u5927\u304D\u306A\u53E3\u3067\u3001\r\n\u30D6\u30E8\u30D6\u30E8\u3057\u3066\u3044\u3066\u2026\u3042\u3001\u89E6\u308B\u3068\r\n\u3042\u3063\u305F\u304B\u3044\u30CB\u30E3\u2026\u2026\u3002\r\n\u2015\u2015\u6587\u7AE0\u306F\u3053\u3053\u3067\u9014\u5207\u308C\u3066\u3044\u308B\u3002\r\n\u6551\u51FA\u3059\u3079\u304F\u3001\u5BFE\u8C61\u306E\u72E9\u731F\u3092\u6C42\u3080\u3002",
        "Target": "\u30D5\u30EB\u30D5\u30EB\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Pale Shadow",
        "Client": "A Felyne\u0027s Journal",
        "Description": "\u0022So...so...cold... Whiskers\r\nfur-ozen... Tail fur-ozen... Paws\u2014\r\nWha...What\u0027s that? A fur-iendly\r\nsmile? So...warm...meow...\r\nEverything...warm\u2014\u0022\r\n(The diary ends there. You feel\r\ncompelled to rescue its owner.)",
        "Target": "Hunt a Khezu",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une ombre p\u00E2le",
        "Client": "Journal de Felyne",
        "Description": "\u0022Il f-fait si froid... J\u0027ai les\r\nm-moustaches gel\u00E9es... Chapristi !\r\nQ-Qu\u0027est ce que c\u0027est que \u00E7-\u00E7a ?\r\nUn s-sourire ? Oooh, il... fait...\r\nsi chaud... si... chaud...\u0022\r\n(Le journal s\u0027arr\u00EAte. Vous sentez\r\nle besoin d\u0027aller sauver son auteur.)",
        "Target": "Chasser un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Un\u0027ombra pallida",
        "Client": "Diario di un Felyne",
        "Description": "\u0022Fa freddo... Tanto freddo.\r\nHo i baffi gelati, la coda\r\ngelata, le zampe... E quello?\r\nUn sorriso amichevole? Fa\r\ncaldo...! Miao, fa tanto...\r\ncal...\u0022 (Il diario finisce\r\nqui e vuoi salvare l\u0027autore.)",
        "Target": "Caccia un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Ein blasser Schatten",
        "Client": "Tagebuch eines Felynen",
        "Description": "\u0022So... so... kalt... Schnurrhaare\r\ngefroren... Schwanz gefroren...\r\nPfoten... Wa-- Was ist das? Ein\r\nheiteres L\u00E4cheln? So... warm...\r\nmiau... Alles... warm--\u0022\r\n(Hier endet der Eintrag. Du\r\nrettest den Schreiber besser.)",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Khezu.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Una sombra p\u00E1lida",
        "Client": "Diario de un Felyne",
        "Description": "\u0022Qu\u00E9 f-f-fr\u00EDo... Los bigotes,\r\nla cola... T-todo congelado...\r\n\u00BFQ-qu\u00E9 es eso? \u00BFUn amigo?\r\nQu\u00E9 c\u00E1lido... Todo es c\u00E1l...\u0022.\r\n(El diario acaba as\u00ED. Sientes\r\nque debes ayudar al autor).",
        "Target": "Caza un Khezu",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
